1
00:00:00,300 --> 00:00:05,300
Lagging Theory is not a delay model.

2
00:00:05,300 --> 00:00:12,000
It tests when gradient and flux fall out of sync.

3
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:20,000
Memory can come from storage, leakage, exchange, or coupling.

4
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:28,000
A fitted curve can still transfer the wrong parameter.

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:36,750
The test is whether pumping limits, recovery time, or risk changes.

6
00:00:36,750 --> 00:00:42,500
Use lag only when it changes the decision.
